// AS3 linkage class `UiHud` is the openfl-swf generated library symbol `Ui_hud` (the SWF symbol's
// library name was snake/lowerCamel; openfl names the class from it, not the AS3 linkage). Alias the
// two so `new UiHud()` constructs the real clip (with its named child instances), not an empty stub.
typedef UiHud = Ui_hud;
